title: I Saw the Light. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2016)
description:
In theaters: March 25th, 2016

Description:

I Saw the Light, the story of legendary country-western singer Hank Williams, who in his brief life created one of the greatest bodies of work in American music. The film chronicles his meteoric rise to fame and its ultimately tragic effect on his health and personal life.

Director: Marc Abraham

Writers: Marc Abraham

Actors: Tom Hiddleston, Elizabeth Olsen, Cherry Jones, Bradley Whitford, Maddie Hasson, Wrenn Schmidt, David Krumholtz

Genre: Drama

Run Time: 2 hours 3 minutes
